rdt-eclipse is a ruby development plugin for the eclipse IDE

DEPENDENCY: eclipse, available from slackbuilds.org

once this is installed, you must 
=> go to 'Prefences'
=> 'Plug-in Development'
=> 'Target Platform'
=> the 'Plug-ins' tab 
=> and 'Add' from 'File-system' this /opt/ecliplse/plugins/org.rubypeople.rdt-* directory
